\begin{align*}
U^T M U &amp;= 
\begin{pmatrix}
\vec{u}_1^T \\
\vec{u}_2^T \\
\vdots \\
\vec{u}_n^T
\end{pmatrix}
M
\begin{pmatrix}
\vec{u}_1 &amp; \vec{u}_2 &amp; \ldots &amp; \vec{u}_n
\end{pmatrix} \\
&amp;= 
\begin{pmatrix}
\vec{u}_1^T M \vec{u}_1 &amp; \vec{u}_1^T M \vec{u}_2 &amp; \ldots &amp; \vec{u}_1^T M \vec{u}_n \\
\vec{u}_2^T M \vec{u}_1 &amp; \vec{u}_2^T M \vec{u}_2 &amp; \ldots &amp; \vec{u}_2^T M \vec{u}_n \\
\vdots &amp; \vdots &amp; \ddots &amp; \vdots \\
\vec{u}_n^T M \vec{u}_1 &amp; \vec{u}_n^T M \vec{u}_2 &amp; \ldots &amp; \vec{u}_n^T M \vec{u}_n
\end{pmatrix}.
\end{align*}
$$

依据$U^T M U = I$, 则

$$
\begin{cases}
\vec{u}_i^T M \vec{u}_i = 1, &amp; \\
\vec{u}_i^T M \vec{u}_j = 0, &amp; \text{for } 0 &lt; i \neq j \leq n
\end{cases}
$$

由

$$
\vec{u}_j^T K \vec{u}_i = \vec{u}_j^T \lambda_i M \vec{u}_i = \lambda_i \vec{u}_j^T M \vec{u}_i \quad (0 &lt; i, j \leq n)
$$

得

$$
\vec{u}_j^T K \vec{u}_i = 
\begin{cases}
\lambda_i, &amp; \text{if } i = j, \\
0, &amp; \text{if } i \neq j.
\end{cases}
$$

所以

$$
U^T K U = \Lambda = 
\begin{pmatrix}
\lambda_1 &amp; 0 &amp; \cdots &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; \lambda_2 &amp; \cdots &amp; 0 \\
\vdots &amp; \vdots &amp; \ddots &amp; \vdots \\
0 &amp; 0 &amp; \cdots &amp; \lambda_n
\end{pmatrix}

$$
\begin{align*}
U^T M U &=
\begin{pmatrix}
\vec{u}_1^T \\
\vec{u}_2^T \\
\vdots \\
\vec{u}_n^T
\end{pmatrix}
M
\begin{pmatrix}
\vec{u}_1 & \vec{u}_2 & \ldots & \vec{u}_n
\end{pmatrix} \\
&=
\begin{pmatrix}
\vec{u}_1^T M \vec{u}_1 & \vec{u}_1^T M \vec{u}_2 & \ldots & \vec{u}_1^T M \vec{u}_n \\
\vec{u}_2^T M \vec{u}_1 & \vec{u}_2^T M \vec{u}_2 & \ldots & \vec{u}_2^T M \vec{u}_n \\
\vdots & \vdots & \ddots & \vdots \\
\vec{u}_n^T M \vec{u}_1 & \vec{u}_n^T M \vec{u}_2 & \ldots & \vec{u}_n^T M \vec{u}_n
\end{pmatrix}.
\end{align*}
$$

依据$U^T M U = I$, 则

$$
\begin{cases}
\vec{u}_i^T M \vec{u}_i = 1, & \\
\vec{u}_i^T M \vec{u}_j = 0, & \text{for } 0 < i \neq j \leq n
\end{cases}
$$

由

$$
\vec{u}_j^T K \vec{u}_i = \vec{u}_j^T \lambda_i M \vec{u}_i = \lambda_i \vec{u}_j^T M \vec{u}_i \quad (0 < i, j \leq n)
$$

得

$$
\vec{u}_j^T K \vec{u}_i =
\begin{cases}
\lambda_i, & \text{if } i = j, \\
0, & \text{if } i \neq j.
\end{cases}
$$

所以

$$
U^T K U = \Lambda =
\begin{pmatrix}
\lambda_1 & 0 & \cdots & 0 \\
0 & \lambda_2 & \cdots & 0 \\
\vdots & \vdots & \ddots & \vdots \\
0 & 0 & \cdots & \lambda_n
\end{pmatrix}
$$
